# xonnel-exit

A python library: xonnel-exit

- supports:
    - sys.exit
    - os._exit
    - atexit

- EXIT.register(call=callable)
    - when the program ends it'll call all these before program ends

## Install

LOCAL:
cd xonnel-exit
pip install -e .

PyPI:
pip install xonnel-exit
